import React from "react";

const Todos = () => {
	return (
		<>
			<form>
				<input 
					type="text" 
					name="fullName" 
					placeholder="Enter a name"
					required="required"
				/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					name="address"
					placeholder="Enter a adress"
					required="required"
				/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					name="phoneNumber"
					placeholder="Enter a phonenumber"
					required="required"
				/>
				<input 
					type="text"
					name="email"
					placeholder="Enter a email"
					required="required"
				/>
				<button type="submit">Add</button>
			</form>
		</>
	);
};

export default Todos;
